PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FAt this meeting, around 50 volunteers
OL,7,Fhave turned up, including more than 15
OL,8,Fnew recruits. Men and women ranging in
OL,9,Fage from their seventies to their
OL,10,Ftwenties.
OL,12,FOperating clandestinely because they
OL,13,Fsay they've been branded 'traitors' by
OL,14,Ftheir opponents and threatened with
OL,15,Fviolent repercussions, including acid
OL,16,Fattacks and rape.
OL,18,FThe reason: they are a pro-migrant
OL,19,Fgroup in the deeply divided town of
OL,20,FCrowborough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FThe government is planning to move
OL,7,Fmore than 500 asylum seekers into a
OL,8,Fformer army camp on the edge of the
OL,9,Fsmall Sussex town. The camp will house
OL,10,Fthe migrants - all men - while a
OL,11,Fdecision is made about their asylum
OL,12,Fapplications.
OL,14,FIt's a controversial move that has led
OL,15,Fto a split amongst residents in
OL,16,FCrowborough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FOn one side, a vocal anti-migrant
OL,7,Fmovement that now holds regular
OL,8,Fprotests and marches. On the other, an
OL,9,Funderground pro-migrant network
OL,10,Forganising donations and workshops for
OL,11,Fthe men.
OL,13,FThe anti-migrant movement has made all
OL,14,Fthe headlines so far. On recent
OL,15,Fmarches hundreds, potentially
OL,16,Fthousands, of people walked through
OL,17,Fthe streets of the town, many waving
OL,18,FUnion flags and chanting anti-
OL,19,Fgovernment slogans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FDespite claims from their detractors,
OL,7,Fmost of the people we encountered were
OL,8,Flocal to Crowborough. Some held strong
OL,9,Fpolitical beliefs that no migrants
OL,10,Fshould be allowed into Britain at all,
OL,11,Fwhile others were keen to emphasize
OL,12,Fthat they had no problem with asylum
OL,13,Fseekers in principle, they were just
OL,14,Fconcerned at 500 unvetted men moving
OL,15,Finto the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,F"I want to be really clear this is not
OL,7,Fabout race, it's about the
OL,8,Fappropriateness of putting ...
OL,9,Funemployed, undocumented men half a
OL,10,Fmile from my children," said one
OL,11,Fmother on a march.
OL,13,F"Why do they have to be within a
OL,14,Fcommunity?," asked another woman.
OL,15,F"They don't speak English, there's
OL,16,Fnothing for them to do around here."
OL,18,FThere are multiple ironies in the
OL,19,Fsituation Crowborough finds itself in.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]uD@AOUvD@LO]wD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FThe first is that the men have only
OL,7,Fbeen moved to the town because the
OL,8,Fgovernment wants to show it is
OL,9,Fstopping migrants being housed in
OL,10,Fhotels - which was the source of
OL,11,Fprotests elsewhere in the country last
OL,12,Fyear. The policy of moving the men to
OL,13,Fan army camp is supposed to show that
OL,14,Fthe government are being tough on
OL,15,Fmigration, but inadvertently it has
OL,16,Fcreated the exact sort of conflict and
OL,17,Fcriticism it had hoped to avoid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FThe second is that the town used to be
OL,7,Fknown as one of the most friendly in
OL,8,Fthe country for asylum seekers. In
OL,9,F2022, residents of Crowborough and
OL,10,Fnearby towns and villages welcomed
OL,11,Faround 600 Ukrainian refugees. Now,
OL,12,Fthe town has become the epicentre of
OL,13,Fthe anti-migrant movement.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FThe third irony is that those anti-
OL,7,Fmigrant protests have actually
OL,8,Fgalvanised some locals to join the pro-
OL,9,Fmigrant network and go out and help
OL,10,Fthe asylum seekers, because they feel
OL,11,Fthe marches don't represent the town.
OL,13,F"These people are human beings and
OL,14,Fthey should be treated like humans,
OL,15,Fnot aliens", said one of the
OL,16,Fvolunteers.
OL,18,FThe underground network, called SAMAS,
OL,19,Fis working on getting permission to
OL,20,Fcarry out their classes and workshops
OL,21,Fin the former army camp.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FFor now their work mostly consists of
OL,7,Fputting together welcome boxes for the
OL,8,Fmen: clean underwear, socks, snacks,
OL,9,Fdeodorant - basic necessities - and a
OL,10,Fnote welcoming them to Crowborough in
OL,11,Fa variety of languages.
OL,13,FThe meetings are spent instructing the
OL,14,Fvolunteers on how to act and
OL,15,Fcommunicate with the asylum seekers,
OL,16,Fplanning music and art workshops,
OL,17,Fpreparing English language classes and
OL,18,Fidentifying who has skills that may
OL,19,Fhelp the men, such as trauma therapy
OL,20,For knowledge of how to grow fruit and
OL,21,Fvegetables.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FOnce fully operational, the network
OL,7,Fwill host events both on-site and off-
OL,8,Fsite, as the asylum seekers are
OL,9,Fallowed to leave the camp.
OL,11,F"We are not encouraging or creating
OL,12,Fthe situation that these men are in,
OL,13,Fwe are just helping them once they are
OL,14,Fhere", says another of the volunteers.
OL,15,F"I don't see how that is being a
OL,16,Ftraitor."
OL,18,FBut according to members of the
OL,19,Fnetwork, that is what they are being
OL,20,Fcalled by the other side.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@EO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773094277
OL,3,CThe underground network helping asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in divided town
OL,6,FAll those who sign up are warned at
OL,7,Ftheir first meeting about the threats.
OL,8,FThe organiser of SAMAS says that
OL,9,Fpeople have had their doors kicked in
OL,10,Fand have been followed and threatened
OL,11,Fin person, as well as online.
OL,13,F"It just takes one disenfranchised
OL,14,Fperson", said the organiser, who wants
OL,15,Fto remain anonymous for his own safety.
OL,17,F"They were talking about raping my
OL,18,Fwife and killing me, that I was the
OL,19,Fproblem in the country"
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@GO]yD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
